<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Article</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .article {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6e4c1f; /* Brown color shade */
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px; /* Changed font size */
        }
        .agree-button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 30px auto 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #6e4c1f; /* Brown color shade */
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .agree-button:hover {
            background-color: #543b14; /* Darker brown color shade on hover */
        }
        .article-image {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="article">
        <img src="images/Picture2.png" alt="Earth" class="article-image">
             <p>
        The ancient wisdom of the Atharvaveda reminds us:
        <i>"Earth is my mother and I am her child."</i>
        This teaches us to love and respect our planet, just like we love and respect our mothers.
    </p>
    <p>
        When we use this application, let's remember this important lesson. Let's not upload fake pictures or videos just for personal gain.
        Instead, let's be honest and responsible, just like good children to our mother Earth.
    </p>
    <p>
        Our goal in using this application should be to show love and gratitude to our planet. Let's protect the environment and keep Earth healthy,
        as our lives depend on it.
    </p>
    <p>
        Together, let's play our part in preserving and cherishing our beautiful Earth.
    </p>
         <a href="registration.jsp" class="agree-button">I AGREE AND GO FOR REGISTRATION </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
